{"tid":962577,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭擅改檢控政策　法律界籲明日上街","createTime":"2018-12-31T03:23:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T11:24:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d0bd32ee9329253bb13c3b918e30604c4db06741","tid":962577,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T03:23:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181231/20580432\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181231%2F20580432&d=LTuk7bByEYVromtWsWAKrMP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=0d502a5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181231%2F20580432&h=1a4b9c91\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181231/20580432</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年12月31日 <br />\n<br />\n鄭擅改檢控政策　法律界籲明日上街<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181231/large/31la4p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181231%2Flarge%2F31la4p3.jpg&h=f7aadfae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】「香港未完蛋，希望在民間」。民陣今年元旦續辦遊行，呼籲市民上街守護庫房、爭取重啟政改、反對政治打壓、堅拒23條及國歌法，亦促檢控涉UGL案的梁振英，明日下午兩點在銅鑼灣東角道集合，再遊行至公民廣場。法政匯思將會參與遊行，召集人吳宗鑾（圖）希望公眾警覺，鄭若驊稱只有涉及律政司同事才會外尋法律意見非單一事件，指鄭所說的政策若成先例，「以後位高權重嘅人牽涉刑事案件，律政司都會以同樣做法（行事）」。<br />\n<br />\n吳宗鑾稱法政匯思將參與遊行，除希望律政司了解法律界訴求，更重要是引起廣泛關注，強調遊行是希望公眾明白律政司不尋求獨立意見「係一個錯嚟」、「唔係佢所講有膊頭有承擔」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：公民廣場「禁獨」　獨派稱續遊行<br />\n<br />\n民陣轟UGL案處理差劣<br />\n<br />\n吳指以往涉及重大公眾利益案件，律政司都外判尋獨立意見，最後由律政司作決定，「我哋認可同支持DOJ（律政司）獨立決策權，係要維持」，但要讓公眾看到有避免官官相衞，「係有嫌疑都唔得」。他強調鄭是政治任命官員，工作性質本身已有利益衝突，故更要讓公眾感到所做決定是獨立於政治外，「如何履行佢（司長）嘅工作，本身已經唔係法律問題，係政治問題」。<br />\n<br />\n法律界立法會議員、公民黨郭榮鏗亦指法律界對鄭的解釋十分嬲怒，「解釋完全唔掂」，偏離律政司一貫做法，他更警告如鄭在下月底的司法及法律事務委員會的回應無法說服公眾，必須進一步在立法會大會向鄭提出不信任動議。民陣召集人岑子杰也呼籲巿民元旦上街，他批評特區政府處理UGL案表現差劣，希望巿民透過遊行表明反對。<br />\n<br />\n■記者梁穎妍、林俊謙  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n僭建地庫　隱瞞銀行　 鄭若驊涉呃按揭　警查一年無下文<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n公民廣場「禁獨」　獨派稱續遊行<br />\n<br />\n公民廣場「禁獨」　獨派稱續遊行<br />\n僭建地庫　隱瞞銀行　鄭若驊涉呃按揭　警查一年無下文"},{"pid":"13b3e5846a04c620e94957e26a4511a06bd47752","tid":962577,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T10:58:02.000Z","msg":"聽日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22f58fc1ab57359d5b8f3e1dd5a7f7c759d3282f","tid":962577,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T10:58:56.000Z","msg":"鄭若驊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n林鄭月娥<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80ac642f5e9f019b3f070d235cbe998cc40c0cfe","tid":962577,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T11:05:59.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n<br />\n14：00 集合<br />\n15：00 起步"},{"pid":"9cdd2b8ced310346539dbda6b26154370e48cea3","tid":962577,"uid":5489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T11:24:02.000Z","msg":"郭承認在北京強力干預下要向外游說存在矛盾，但他指香港仍值得擁有有別內地的關稅區，原因是<span style=\"color: red;\">香港司法制度仍然獨立</span>，只是外在因素正在扭曲司法制度<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁你就咪撚干預司法獨立啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e78adb167946bde0f3ca61acc933c6dd6d05362f","tid":962577,"uid":5489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T11:24:59.000Z","msg":"郭榮鏗唔信焦土論 信司法仍獨立倡力保政策法<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181208/59004507\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181208%2F59004507&d=LTuk7bByEYVromtWsWAKrMP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=2d67a27f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181208%2F59004507&h=595c1f31\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181208/59004507</a>"}]}